    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Extinct order of aquatic reptiles with slender elongate jaws filled with long pointed teeth, a tail as long as or longer than the body and flattened side to side, well developed limbs, and enlarged paddlelike hind feet.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
